[0m[49m[39m  183, 183[0m:[39m[49m | **Amazon Neptune** | Graph database storing provider, location, network, and specialty nodes with relationship edges |
[0m[49m[39m  184, 184[0m:[39m[49m | **AWS Glue** | ETL pipeline for ingesting, reconciling, and transforming provider data from multiple sources |
[0m[49m[39m  185, 185[0m:[39m[49m | **Amazon S3** | Staging area for source files and Neptune bulk load format; archive for historical snapshots |
[0m[49m[39m  186, 186[0m:[39m[49m | **AWS Lambda** | Query API layer translating search requests into graph traversals |
