[0m[49m[39m  193, 193[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  194, 194[0m:[39m[49m ### Code
[0m[49m[39m  195, 195[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  196, 196[0m:[39m[49m > **Reference implementations:** The following AWS resources demonstrate the patterns used in this recipe:
